name: Some Kind Of Winter - old V2

metadata.name: Drool
metadata.description:
A skinny birch tree in between of frozen fellas who are drooling over it's beautiful silver bark and it's elegantly and delicately shaped branches.

I discovered this patch of woodland right next to the street this summer when I  was travelling from Austria to Germany to visit my family who lives there. It was obvious that I had to come back there some early morning when there was potential for hoar frost and fog.  

The collector will reveive a hand signed fine art print of this NFT, sized ca. 40x30cm.
